Name: Average time for Completed + Resolved when preceded by Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time for Completed + Resolved when not preceded by Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call does not occur

Name: Total time for Completed + Resolved in variants that include Completed + In Call versus variants that do not include Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Minimum time for Completed + Resolved following Completed + In Call within the same case
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Time from Completed + In Call to Completed + Resolved in cases where both activities occur consecutively
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration of Completed + Resolved grouped by country, specifically for cases that passed through Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Completed + Resolved in process variants that contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Cycle time of Completed + Resolved in the most frequent variant that includes Completed + In Call (Accepted + In Progress → Accepted + In Progress → Completed + In Call)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Time from case start to Completed + Resolved in traces that include Completed + In Call compared to traces that end directly with Completed + Resolved without any wait states
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Duration of Completed + Resolved when it directly follows Accepted + In Progress versus when it follows a waiting activity (e.g., Accepted + Wait - User, Accepted + Wait - Vendor, or Accepted + Wait - Implementation)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time spent in Completed + Resolved across all variants that transition from Completed + In Call to Completed + Resolved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time between Completed + In Call and Completed + Resolved across all cases where both activities appear in sequence
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time for Completed + Resolved in variants that loop through Accepted + In Progress multiple times before reaching Completed + Resolved, with and without an intermediate Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Time from the last occurrence of Accepted + In Progress to Completed + Resolved in cases that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Cycle time of Completed + Resolved in variants originating from Queued + Awaiting Assignment and containing Completed + In Call versus those that do not contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'
